25-27 April - No Bake Cheesecake

- 1/3 cup margarine or butter
- 1 cup graham cracker crumbs OR graham cracker crumbs
- 1/4 cup sugar 
- 8 oz cream cheese
- 22 oz lemon pie filling
- 8 oz carton cool whip or whipped cream

Place butter in 8 or 9" square microwave pan. Microwave on High 1 minute or until melted. Add crumbs and sugar, stir to mix. Press into bottom of pan. Remove foil wrapper from cream cheese. Microwave on LOW 40-60 seconds, until softened. Beat cream cheese until fluffy, beat in lemon filling. Fold in whipped topping. Spoon into crust. Quick chill in freezer for 30 minutes or refrigerate. 